 ros-one-plotjuggler-ros - PlotJuggler plugin for ROS
Changes:
 ros-one-plotjuggler-ros (1.7.3-2-g234ceaa-2024.01.31.19.31) jammy; urgency=high
 .
   * Fix mapping of multiple pal_statistics topics (#61 <https://github.com/PlotJuggler/plotjuggler-ros-plugins/issues/61>)
   * fix implicit uint8_t -> double narrowing (#42 <https://github.com/PlotJuggler/plotjuggler-ros-plugins/issues/42>)
     YES, the standard committee believes this might be narrowing
     and clang 12 throws this error:
     > error: non-constant-expression cannot be narrowed from type 'uint8_t' (aka 'unsigned char') to 'double' in initializer list [-Wc++11-narrowing]
   * Contributors: Michael Görner, Victor Lopez
